The paper discusses the use of directional mmWave small cells for improving network capacity, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also proposes a relay path selection algorithm and a multi-hop transmission scheduling algorithm, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The issue of blockage in mmWave communications is a security concern (cs.CR), and the proposed scheme involves optimizing network performance (cs.SY).
